localString.value: Welcome to the El'lar d'Ssinssrigg, <lad/lass>. Something I can do for ya?
You'll have to talk to Flo for that. She's our waitress and will be glad to help you out. Just yell out Barmaid and tell her what you want. That should get her attention.

Well, we have two different kinds of rooms here at El'lar d'Ssinssrigg, our regular rooms, and then rooms for those that aren't well off but still need a place to rest. Which room would ya like to know about?

Well, <boy/girl>, you get what you pay for in these rooms. We have four of these rooms and each costs only 5 gold pieces to rent. Ya can fit three people into each room. It's a real bargain but I can't guarantee a good nights sleep.
We have four regular rooms here at the Purple Rose and each sleeps two. They have everything you expect to see in an inn and can be rented for only 15 gold pieces.
What room do you wish to make occupied?
What room needs to be reset?

This Inn is based off of the Purple Rose Inn Scripts by Russell S. Ahlstrom (Judoth Dar'nir). For more information about the Purple Rose Inn or to download it (and updates to it) visit <StartAction>http://www.woventapestry.net/NWN/purplerose.html</Start>.
I'd like something to eat and drink.
I would like to rent a room.
I changed my mind. I don't want a room.
I only have enough money for your cheapest room.
Just a regular room, if you will.
Explain the different kind of rooms to me, please.
I'd like to purchase a room now.
Let's hear about your budget rooms.
Let's hear about your regular rooms.
